          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/2371271/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '2371271', 'pos': 9, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})" class="">
            預知生命大蛻變：由恐懼走向愛的靈...
          </a>
        </dd>
      </dl>
        <dl class="clear"></dl>
  </div>
