    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5125506/" class="title-link">从大方向转变视角的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5125506"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3930693/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3930693-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3930693/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小米</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-10-09"
      class="main-meta">2011-10-09 10:26:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5125506_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  从大方向转变视角的书，可以说是蹭蹭蹭好几个层次的提升。我看这本是为了配合《奇迹课程》，总之很不错。但有些地方不能完全认同。也许正如奇迹课程所说的：你们不必相信，只需去运用……书中的有些观点甚至会引起你们强烈的反感…… 却是，有些老反感了。咋办腻？ 宽恕吧。 

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
